      "writtenOn": "2020-01-23T19:09:25Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "FWIU this will grow a lot (TODOs). Do we have to have this layer of indirection? Can we put Module in server package and pass *server.Server in Module.Initialize?",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 63,
        "startChar": 0,
        "endLine": 93,
